Using Turing.jl to find the optimal price

We are goint to model the relationship between quantity and price using the equation: Q = aPc. The priors of a and c are modeled as a cauchy distribution and Q is modeled as a poisson distribution.

xxxxxxxxxx
md"### Using Turing.jl to find the optimal price
1.4 ms

In order to linearize the model, we apply Log function in both sides of the equation:

Log(E(Q|P)) = Log(a) + c * Log(P)

xxxxxxxxxx
